.ft C
$ salt\-sproxy \(aq*\(aq \-\-preview\-target
\- edge1.seattle
\- edge1.vancouver
\- edge1.atlanta
\- edge2.atlanta
\- edge1.raleigh
\- edge1.la
\- edge1.sfo

# get the LLDP neighbors from all the edge devices
$ salt\-sproxy \(aqedge*\(aq net.lldp
